---
import Layout from "../layouts/Layout.astro";
---

<Layout title="Eric Alex | Formi Case Study">
  <main class="case-study-page">
    
    <section class="project-hero">
      <div class="hero-content">
        <p class="project-category">Videography & Marketing</p>
        <h1 class="project-title">Formi</h1>
        <p class="project-tagline">Building an educational podcast channel to connect founders, brand managers, and marketing experts.</p>
      </div>
    </section>

    <section class="meta-section">
      <div class="meta-grid">
        <div class="meta-item">
          <h3>Role</h3>
          <p>Marketing Coordinator</p>
        </div>
        <div class="meta-item">
          <h3>Duration</h3>
          <p>6 Weeks (Internship)</p>
        </div>
        <div class="meta-item">
          <h3>Location</h3>
          <p>Bangalore, Karnataka</p>
        </div>
        <div class="meta-item">
          <h3>Focus</h3>
          <p>Podcast Production</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <section class="content-section">
      
      <div class="content-block">
        <h2>The Objective</h2>
        <p>
          Formi brought me on board during the early stages of developing an educational podcast channel. 
          The goal was to build an audience by interviewing founders and experts from various companies, 
          delving into business topics to provide valuable insights for viewers.
        </p>
        <div style="margin-top: 1.5rem; display: flex; gap: 1.5rem;">
           <a href="https://www.instagram.com/formi.co.in/" target="_blank" class="social-link">Instagram ↗</a>
           <a href="https://www.youtube.com/@experience-formi" target="_blank" class="social-link">YouTube ↗</a>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="content-block">
        <h2>The Approach</h2>
        <p>
          As the Videography and Marketing Coordinator, I was responsible for the end-to-end execution of the podcast.
          My senior colleague managed the guest lineup via Excel, while I handled the technical execution.
        </p>
        <div class="bullet-grid">
          <div class="bullet-card">
            <h3>Production</h3>
            <p>Managed shooting setups for in-person interviews and utilized Riverside for remote recording sessions to ensure high-quality audio and video.</p>
          </div>
          <div class="bullet-card">
            <h3>Editing Strategy</h3>
            <p>Edited podcasts with a focus on keeping them short, interesting, and educational to maintain viewer retention throughout the episode.</p>
          </div>
          <div class="bullet-card">
            <h3>Optimization</h3>
            <p>Utilized Meta Business Suite to optimize and promote content effectively across social channels.</p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="content-block highlighted-block">
        <h2>Optimized Workflow</h2>
        <p class="block-intro">
          To maximize efficiency during the six-week program, I implemented a streamlined editing process using AI tools.
        </p>
        
        <ul class="detailed-list">
          <li>
            <strong>Simultaneous Content Creation:</strong> While editing the long-form podcasts, I tracked and isolated engaging segments in real-time to create Reels, significantly speeding up the delivery pipeline.
          </li>
          <li>
            <strong>AI-Assisted Editing:</strong> I utilized <strong>Descript</strong> to edit podcasts via text/transcript, which accelerated the rough-cut process word-by-word.
          </li>
          <li>
            <strong>Final Output:</strong> Produced <strong>6 full-length podcasts</strong> and approximately <strong>45 Instagram Reels</strong> during the internship.
          </li>
        </ul>
      </div>

      <div class="content-block">
        <h2>Visuals & Recognition</h2>
        <div class="visuals-grid">
          
          <div class="visual-item">
            <div class="image-frame">
              <img src="/assets/formi-youtube.png" alt="Formi YouTube Channel" />
            </div>
            <p class="caption">YouTube Channel Strategy</p>
          </div>

          <div class="visual-item">
            <div class="image-frame">
              <img src="/assets/formi-insta.png" alt="Formi Instagram Reels" />
            </div>
            <p class="caption">Instagram Reels Growth</p>
          </div>

          <div class="visual-item">
            <div class="image-frame">
              <img src="/assets/formi-certificate.png" alt="Internship Certificate" />
            </div>
            <p class="caption">Certificate of Excellence</p>
          </div>

        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="content-block">
        <h2>Outcomes & Reflection</h2>
        <p>
          Although the campaign was paused due to unforeseen reasons, the content was beginning to gain traction, with Reels averaging <strong>300 views</strong> organically.
        </p>
        <p>
          I concluded the internship with high marks and a certificate of excellence. The team characterized my performance as enthusiastic and dedicated. As my first corporate internship, it provided a wealth of learning about corporate life and structured guidance from senior leadership.
        </p>
      </div>

      <div class="content-block">
        <h2>Tools & Tech Stack</h2>
        <div class="tech-tags">
          <span>Adobe Premiere Pro</span>
          <span>Riverside</span>
          <span>Descript</span>
          <span>Meta Business Suite</span>
          <span>Microsoft Excel</span>
          <span>Planning and Organising</span>
          <span>Creativity</span>
        </div>
      </div>

    </section>

    <div class="project-footer">
      <a href="/work" class="back-link">&larr; Back to Work</a>
    </div>

  </main>
</Layout>

<style>
  .case-study-page {
    width: 100%;
    max-width: 1200px; 
    margin: 0 auto;
    padding: 0 2.5rem 4rem 2.5rem;
  }

  /* HERO */
  .project-hero {
    padding: 8rem 0 4rem 0;
    border-bottom: 1px solid var(--border-color);
  }
  
  .project-category {
    font-size: 0.9rem;
    color: #FF4444; 
    text-transform: uppercase;
    letter-spacing: 0.05em;
    margin-bottom: 1rem;
  }

  .project-title {
    font-size: 3.5rem;
    font-weight: 500;
    margin: 0 0 1rem 0;
    line-height: 1.1;
    color: var(--text-color);
  }

  .project-tagline {
    font-size: 1.5rem;
    color: var(--light-text-color);
    line-height: 1.4;
    max-width: 700px;
  }

  /* METADATA GRID */
  .meta-section {
    padding: 2rem 0;
    border-bottom: 1px solid var(--border-color);
  }

  .meta-grid {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: repeat(4, 1fr);
    gap: 2rem;
  }

  .meta-item h3 {
    font-size: 0.85rem;
    color: var(--light-text-color);
    text-transform: uppercase;
    margin: 0 0 0.5rem 0;
  }

  .meta-item p {
    font-size: 1rem;
    color: var(--text-color);
    font-weight: 500;
    margin: 0;
  }

  /* CONTENT SECTIONS */
  .content-section {
    padding-top: 4rem;
  }

  .content-block {
    margin-bottom: 5rem;
  }

  .content-block h2 {
    font-size: 2rem;
    margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
    color: var(--text-color);
  }

  .content-block p {
    font-size: 1.1rem;
    line-height: 1.7;
    color: var(--light-text-color);
    margin-bottom: 1rem;
    max-width: 800px;
  }

  .social-link {
    color: #FF4444;
    text-decoration: none;
    font-weight: 500;
    border-bottom: 1px solid transparent;
    transition: border-color 0.3s;
  }
  .social-link:hover {
    border-bottom-color: #FF4444;
  }

  /* BULLET GRID CARDS */
  .bullet-grid {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: repeat(3, 1fr);
    gap: 1.5rem;
    margin-top: 2rem;
  }

  .bullet-card {
    background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.03);
    border: 1px solid var(--border-color);
    padding: 2rem;
    border-radius: 8px;
  }

  .bullet-card h3 {
    font-size: 1.2rem;
    color: var(--text-color);
    margin: 0 0 1rem 0;
  }

  .bullet-card p {
    font-size: 1rem;
    line-height: 1.5;
    margin: 0;
    color: var(--light-text-color);
  }

  /* HIGHLIGHTED BLOCK */
  .highlighted-block {
    background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.03); 
    padding: 3rem;
    border-radius: 12px;
    border: 1px solid var(--border-color);
  }

  .detailed-list {
    list-style: none;
    padding: 0;
    margin-top: 2rem;
  }

  .detailed-list li {
    position: relative;
    padding-left: 1.5rem;
    margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
    font-size: 1.1rem;
    line-height: 1.6;
    color: var(--light-text-color);
  }

  .detailed-list li::before {
    content: "•";
    position: absolute;
    left: 0;
    color: #FF4444; 
    font-size: 1.5rem;
    line-height: 1.2rem;
  }

  .detailed-list strong {
    color: var(--text-color);
  }

  /* NEW: VISUALS GRID */
  .visuals-grid {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: repeat(3, 1fr);
    gap: 2rem;
    margin-top: 2rem;
  }

  .visual-item {
    text-align: center;
  }

  .image-frame {
    width: 100%;
    aspect-ratio: 16/10; /* Standard screenshot shape */
    background-color: #222;
    border: 1px solid var(--border-color);
    border-radius: 8px;
    overflow: hidden;
    margin-bottom: 1rem;
    transition: transform 0.3s ease;
  }
  
  .image-frame:hover {
    transform: translateY(-5px);
  }

  .image-frame img {
    width: 100%;
    height: 100%;
    object-fit: cover;
  }

  .caption {
    font-size: 0.9rem;
    color: var(--light-text-color);
  }


  /* TECH TAGS */
  .tech-tags {
    display: flex;
    flex-wrap: wrap;
    gap: 1rem;
  }

  .tech-tags span {
    border: 1px solid var(--border-color);
    padding: 0.5rem 1rem;
    border-radius: 20px;
    font-size: 0.9rem;
    color: var(--light-text-color);
  }

  /* FOOTER */
  .project-footer {
    margin-top: 6rem;
    padding-top: 2rem;
    border-top: 1px solid var(--border-color);
  }

  .back-link {
    font-size: 1.1rem;
    color: var(--text-color);
    text-decoration: none;
    transition: color 0.3s;
  }

  .back-link:hover {
    color: #FF4444;
  }

  /* MOBILE STYLES */
  @media (max-width: 768px) {
    .project-hero {
      padding: 6rem 0 3rem 0;
    }
    .project-title {
      font-size: 2.5rem;
    }
    .project-tagline {
      font-size: 1.2rem;
    }
    .meta-grid {
      grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr; 
      gap: 1.5rem;
    }
    .bullet-grid {
      grid-template-columns: 1fr;
    }
    .visuals-grid {
      grid-template-columns: 1fr; /* Stack images on mobile */
      gap: 2rem;
    }
    .highlighted-block {
      padding: 1.5rem;
    }
  }
</style>